python3-bigbluebutton is a Python 3 module (and some scripts) to work
with a Big Blue Button video conferencing system.

Usage of the module:

    import bigbluebutton

Available scripts:

    bbb-get-meetings   List currently running meetings on the local BBB server.
    bbb-shared-notes   Read or write a meeting's etherpad shared notes
                       (text or HTML; --read or --write).

Both scripts run unprivileged and can be used by any user on the system.

Admin command (root):

    bbb-shared-notes-setup
                       Create the unprivileged 'bbb_query' Postgres role
                       (SELECT-only on "sharedNotes") used by
                       bbb-shared-notes.  Run automatically by the package
                       postinst; re-run manually if BigBlueButton was
                       installed after this package.
